title: Grateful Dead Live at Warfield Theater on 1980-10-06

Acoustic Set

Truckin' >

Encore:
U.S. Blues
Comment

Brent Mydland - Keyboards

Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
